OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FOur office is close to the American
OL,8,Fembassy, and three doors down from
OL,9,Fwhere President Trump will be staying
OL,10,Fwhile he's in Beijing, so the place is
OL,11,Fheaving with security.
OL,13,FWe saw more than 100 police officers
OL,14,Fand security personnel lined up for a
OL,15,Fbriefing on Tuesday afternoon, and now
OL,16,Fsoldiers and police are stationed on
OL,17,Fevery corner and crossing in the area.
OL,18,FSecurity scanners have also been set
OL,19,Fup around the periphery of the
OL,20,Fcompound containing Donald Trump's
OL,21,Fhotel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FAs his arrival nears, we've seen a
OL,8,Fbuild-up of guards along all of the
OL,9,Froads the US president and his
OL,10,Fentourage are expected to travel. The
OL,11,F'beast', as the president's car is
OL,12,Fcalled, has already been spotted in
OL,13,Fthe Chinese capital.
OL,15,FI have never seen a security operation
OL,16,Flike this for the visit of a foreign
OL,17,Fstate leader. But of course, Trump is
OL,18,Fno ordinary leader, and this is no
OL,19,Fordinary summit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FPresident Trump and President Xi are
OL,8,Fthe two most powerful men on the
OL,9,Fplanet, and the US-China relationship
OL,10,Fhas been described as the most
OL,11,Fconsequential in the world.
OL,13,FThe stakes couldn't be higher with
OL,14,Ftrade, tech supremacy, nuclear power
OL,15,Fand the future of Taiwan all up for
OL,16,Fdiscussion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FIt's been almost nine years since a US
OL,8,Fpresident last visited China, which
OL,9,Fwas Trump during his first term. Biden
OL,10,Fdidn't make it to Beijing, partly due
OL,11,Fto China's extended Covid lockdown and
OL,12,Fdiplomatic disagreements. Does anyone
OL,13,Fremember the weather balloon?
OL,15,FAnd up until it was confirmed by the
OL,16,FChinese Government on Monday, this
OL,17,Fvisit had been shrouded in
OL,18,Funcertainty, postponed from March due
OL,19,Fto the conflict in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FAlready, both sides appear to agree
OL,8,Fthat a priority at this meeting is to
OL,9,Fextend the trade truce the two leaders
OL,10,Fagreed last October. That came after
OL,11,Fmonths of a spiralling tit-for-tat
OL,12,Fthat saw more than 100% tariffs
OL,13,Fimposed by each side, and China
OL,14,Fthreatening to cut off rare earth
OL,15,Fsupplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FTravelling with Trump are some of
OL,8,FAmerica's top CEO's, including Tim
OL,9,FCook of Apple, Jensen Huang of the
OL,10,Fchip maker Nvidia and Elon Musk, who
OL,11,Fappears to be back in favour. Musk and
OL,12,Fthe Tesla brand are popular in China,
OL,13,Fwith a mega-factory in Shanghai.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FBy bringing a cadre of CEO's with him,
OL,8,FTrump is clearly hoping to do some
OL,9,Fdeals. But for Beijing, it will also
OL,10,Fexemplify how US companies such as
OL,11,FApple and Tesla have enjoyed success
OL,12,Fin China, while restrictions remain on
OL,13,Ftheir Chinese counterparts, like
OL,14,FHuawei and BYD, from entering the
OL,15,FAmerican market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
