PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FTaiwan, a red line issue for Beijing,
OL,8,Fwill also be top of the agenda. Xi
OL,9,FJinping is not happy with the
OL,10,Fmultimillion-dollar arms sales Trump
OL,11,Fapproved for the island, despite that
OL,12,Fbeing a long-established arrangement
OL,13,Funder the US Taiwan Relations Act
OL,14,F(1979).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FThe White House insists its position
OL,8,Fon Taiwan has not changed, but we are
OL,9,Fwatching carefully to see whether Xi
OL,10,FJinping can exact any concessions.
OL,11,FNamely, whether the Americans will
OL,12,Fagree to a change in wording from "not
OL,13,Fsupporting" to "opposing" Taiwan
OL,14,Findependence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FA seemingly innocuous change that
OL,8,Fcould have significant consequences.
OL,9,FNot only would it breach the six
OL,10,Fassurances made by President Reagan in
OL,11,F1982 regarding US commitments to
OL,12,FTaiwan, but it would also signal an
OL,13,Falignment with China's view that
OL,14,FTaiwan is a breakaway province, a huge
OL,15,Fwin for Xi that would weaken Taiwan's
OL,16,Fposition.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
