OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778716978
OL,3,CTehran, trade and Taiwan: Key issues
OL,4,Cas Trump and Xi set for high-stakes
OL,5,Csummit
OL,7,FThe US-Iran war will also loom large
OL,8,Fover the summit. Trump is expected to
OL,9,Freiterate his call for China to help
OL,10,Fget Tehran to do a deal that would
OL,11,Freopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FIran's foreign minister was in Beijing
OL,14,Flast week, presenting the Iranian side
OL,15,Fof the story.
OL,17,FTrump was hoping this visit would be
OL,18,Fon the back of a great victory in the
OL,19,FMiddle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
